{"tid":1277984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"談判開始！川普：協議不能對等 要讓美國佔上風","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T00:46:03.000Z","uid":141151,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8ecbfcfffd6c0df2ad912b5d2b52e158bec5438f","tid":1277984,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"談判開始！川普：協議不能對等 要讓美國佔上風<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2839759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2839759&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=01294053\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2839759&h=59401d36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2839759</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕G20峰會結束，美中貿易同意暫時休兵。美國總統川普週一再表示，與中國的貿易談判已經展開，但強調協議必須以美國利益為優先。<br />\n<br />\n根據《CNBC》報導，川普於白宮向記者表示，目前正與中國進行電話協商，並指出兩國間的任何協議，都需要以美國利益為優先。<br />\n<br />\n川普說道：「他們（美中貿易代表）在電話上談了非常多，之後也打算會面。基本上，貿易談判已經開始了。」。<br />\n<br />\n但川普也補充：「這次協議必須對美國更有利，因為中國在這方面享有優勢已經很多年了。」，他指出，中國對美方的貿易順差已「足夠」，此次美中協議勢必不能對等，必須是1項「讓美國佔上風」的協議。"},{"pid":"664cac6dbe2dbff305d02ba9d18eb42c04c2ad7e","tid":1277984,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a229e6116b0c304d4207e14653ab900f61ba7f","tid":1277984,"uid":255264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"1項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728299bb42d2740e05ac60d533a6fb42d5036c11","tid":1277984,"uid":95520,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"